{"tid":1703834,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"小妹晚飯食自己，答左人幾個問題跟住佢幫我埋單...","createTime":"2019-11-10T12:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T09:20:43.000Z","uid":311922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"88a43fc31226cd14a2a2f04bfeff7bd1eb6a0c0c","tid":1703834,"uid":311922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:39:20.000Z","msg":"話說今晚要食自己  本身已經好褶  一個人去譚仔同人搭枱食清湯米線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對面有個呀叔突然問我食既係咪清湯 我話係<br />\n聽到佢同隔離講下次揀清湯呢次太辣  <br />\n我見佢地食辣食到面都紅晒狂飲檸茶  <br />\n就問佢地食幾辣  有分辣 佢地話1小同普通辣<br />\n跟住我話飲多d水啦咁  對面就拎我張單睇 以為佢想睇價錢  點知拎住企起身埋單  我即刻話唔洗  佢答佢地係食家  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n心唸？？（黑人問號）關咩事？？ 睇佢地又唔似大陸人<br />\n佢邊埋單邊喃喃自語咩清湯<br />\n隔離枱個女人係咁望過黎<br />\n咩事？無功不受祿 我唔覺有咩幫到佢地喎 ？？"},{"pid":"a42a5f58daf6412aaf5eee8a357416e1e302160d","tid":1703834,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 可能米芝連嗰類?"},{"pid":"3fce1b6da0268bfc79076be5eb9371a082eae3d8","tid":1703834,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:43:42.000Z","msg":"神秘顧客？"},{"pid":"26b16dc2f4f3033eb2c642a20f2d52fc1c10f949","tid":1703834,"uid":311922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a42a5f58daf6412aaf5eee8a357416e1e302160d","tid":1703834,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 可能米芝連嗰類?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:44:30.000Z","msg":"米芝連..食譚仔<img s